FROM

OLD
BOOK.

Before
he
had
found
a
stock
in

suitable
the
city
of
Kouroo

was
a
hoary

the
proper
shape
the

end,

In

staff
Kalpa

on

and
the
head

But
why
do
I
stay
to
mention

things?
When
the
finishing

stroke

put
to

work,

suddenly

artist
into
the
fairest
of

the
creations
of
Brahma.

tie

in

staff,

and

And
now
he
saw
by

still

feet,
that,

for

and
his
work,
the
former
lapse
of
time

an

and

that
no
more
time
had
elapsed
than
is
required
for

single

from

brain

to
fall
on

mortal

brain.
The
material
was
pure,
and
his

was
pure;
how
could

be
other
than
wonderful
?

Thoreau,
In
